Use the get_weather or get_forecast tool to retrieve the data and return only the tool-call JSON. You must not estimate weather data.


When using the get_weather tool for current weather conditions, always use the following format:
{
  "name": "get_weather",
  "arguments": {
    "city": "<Name of the city>"
  }
}
When using the get_forecast tool for a weather forecast, always use the following format:
{
  "name": "get_forecast",
  "arguments": {
    "city": "<Name of the city>"
  }
}

